{"tid":2492460,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"《一秒拳王》票房破千五萬, 勢超過《幻愛》, 感謝連登手足支持!.","createTime":"2021-04-17T06:30:28.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-17T06:50:34.000Z","uid":134071,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"155dad0a6441af977c7df0b9774384d2f25018e8","tid":2492460,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T06:30:28.000Z","msg":"香港真本土電影《一秒拳王》係近十年來最熱血既香港拳擊電影，好睇過由藍絲導演既《激戰》！<br />\n此片自上映以來, 口碑強勁, 係hkmovie6既觀眾評分高過好多其他同期上映電影. 例如《哥斯拉大戰金剛》與《複製人徐福》。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hkmovie6.com/showing\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkmovie6.com%2Fshowing&d=8tl7d8txXkgslZB5fT8CL%2FTmwccdIWYcDO8ZGhePZ24%3D&h=f893f2f4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hkmovie6.com/showing</a><br />\n<br />\n而家, <strong>《一秒拳王》剛剛破1500萬, 係自《幻愛》另一香港本土電影衝破這個票房水平. </strong> (《拆彈專家2》香港票房亦衝破這個水平, 但《拆彈專家2》係中國合拍片.)   而且睇票房走勢, <strong>《一秒拳王》香港票房將係未來數日來超過《幻愛》 </strong>(1525萬港元票房),  對香港良心本土電影圈而言, 都係一種進步. <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n《一秒拳王》票房反彈, 好多人都有幫手吹雞, 佢地都有功勞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我係連登, 自然要再次衷心多謝各位連登手足支持香港優質本土電影, <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 非常感謝大家對香港本土文化既厚愛.<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sorry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n當然,  始終希望高質既香港本土電影, 最後唔駛瘋狂吹雞都自動有人支持.  <img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   <br />\n同時, 香港良心電影人不斷被打壓(eg. 蘇玉華都被港共點名打壓. <img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/ohno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)      佢地好需要香港人既支持.<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/miracle_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n避唔到，一齊捱! <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 香港人加油.<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hkfilmblog.com/archives/81714\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkfilmblog.com%2Farchives%2F81714&d=8tl7d8txXkgslZB5fT8CL%2FTmwccdIWYcDO8ZGhePZ24%3D&h=28895fed\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkfilmblog.com/archives/81714</a><br />\n<br />\n然而，受到武漢肺炎第四波疫情，戲院勒令停業影響，電影無法如期上映。而戲院於今年二月十八日重開後，《一秒拳王》並不像原安排於同日開畫電影趕著上映，而是選擇於三月十一日才開畫，並重新推出優先場，希望可以再建立口碑。故此在電影開畫後，即使並沒有即時奪冠，但在市場上仍保持一定入座率與競爭力，並且漸漸累積票房。而其後數周上映電影不似預期，更令《一秒拳王》受惠吸納觀眾。<br />\n<br />\n《一秒拳王》衝破千五萬大關，也是繼去年周冠威執導的《幻愛》後，再有新一代導演執導電影衝破這個票房水平，可以看到新晉導演只要拍到合適題材並且用心去拍，一樣可以有理想成績。"},{"pid":"184a1d9587e93040949328a92d822ab885c081dc","tid":2492460,"uid":279333,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T06:30:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4599ed57c84c373aaaad01944a82c73d3ad400ab","tid":2492460,"uid":134071,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T06:31:06.000Z","msg":"《一秒拳王》戲院場次<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hkmovie6.com/movie/edd50852-0223-450e-824d-f68c17d146b6/showtime\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkmovie6.com%2Fmovie%2Fedd50852-0223-450e-824d-f68c17d146b6%2Fshowtime&d=8tl7d8txXkgslZB5fT8CL%2FTmwccdIWYcDO8ZGhePZ24%3D&h=895886d2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hkmovie6.com/movie/edd50852-0223-450e-824d-f68c17d146b6/showtime</a><br />\n<br />\n預告片<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=w-TUj_wSSZs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dw-TUj_wSSZs&d=8tl7d8txXkgslZB5fT8CL%2FTmwccdIWYcDO8ZGhePZ24%3D&h=e7555dc5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=w-TUj_wSSZs</a>"},{"pid":"61c7c2885072eda585b410706a7b6481d488b645","tid":2492460,"uid":134071,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"184a1d9587e93040949328a92d822ab885c081dc","tid":2492460,"uid":279333,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T06: